features: UNIVERSAL DESIGN: Rigorously safety tested and UL listed, Our ultra strong TV mount fits most 23"-55" TVs weighing up to 99lbs including LG, Sony, Vizio, Panasonic, Toshiba, Sharp, Philips and more. Solid and sturdy TV bracket with compatible faceplate that fits VESA patterns from 100x100mm to 400x400mm. Can be conveniently mounted on 8" or 16" wood stud walls and concrete/brick walls. Please check the VESA pattern of your TV before purchasing.Please do not install on drywall alone,

SAVE SPACE AND ANTI GLARING: Our TV wall mount sits a mere 1.3“ to the wall for a low-profile modern look. Features 0-8° tilt allows you to direct the screen down to reduce glare and improve your viewing angle.So you can choose the most comfortable position while reducing glare and neck/eye strain.

SAFE AND SECURE: This tilt TV wall mount has an open wall plate design that allows you to mount it directly over electrical outlets for a super clean installation. Pulling straps can help you locks and releasesTV breezily and the elegant panel edges prevent your TV from slipping off.
EASY INSTALLATION: With all required mounting hardware and a detailed instruction manual, they will helps you to install this TV wall mount without any hassle.

Friendly After-sales Service - our TV wall mount is constructed from high quality steel materials, we are so confident in the construction, strength and durability of this wall bracket. Please feel free to contact us anytime, rain or shine:-)

reviews.reviewText: Stand came with all hardware and had a few options for different diameter screws to match the back of the TV. reviews.reviewTitle: The ease of installation of this wall mount was a pleasant surprise
reviews.reviewText: I opted for the wall mount in order to free up space in my room while benefiting from an optimal viewing angle for my television. My expectations were simple: easy installation and reliable performance.The ease of installation of this wall mount was a pleasant surprise. Even without being a DIY expert, I managed to put it together quickly. The instructions were clear, and all the necessary parts were included. It really made the process easier.

Pros:- Made of high-quality steel, ensuring sturdiness and reliability.- Includes all necessary accessories, making installation hassle-free.- Clear instruction booklet with diagrams for easy DIY installation.- Swivel function adds a valuable feature for adjusting TV viewing angles.Cons:- Extremely snug fit for a 50" TV, providing little room for upscaling to a larger TV.- Limited future flexibility in terms of TV size upgrades.Overall, this TV wall mount is a great choice for your 50" TV, offering durability, clear instructions, and a useful swivel function. However, if you plan to upgrade to a larger TV in the future, you may need to consider a different mount with more room for adjustment.
